        <p> OLD HOSTEL
            This hostel is the oldest and actually rich hostel in G.W.P, Patna,famous for its immense culture
            ,participation and alumni.The unity among the residents is never lasting here people enjoying being a part
            of the G.W.P’s Hostel.
            Senior’s encouragement fills up the enthusiam in all the activites with the great spark to serve top
            position for the hostel’s pride.
            The respect of the seniors is always increased love and mutual understanding,enhancinh the fun,participation
            and learning.
            Freshers party,Art workshop, wall painting competition,Quizzes on the hostel campus successfully with
            significant partition.
            The quality participation was immense,and the step-wise achievements encouraged the participants to give
            their best.

